T1  - From virtuous to vicious cycles – towards a life cycle model of technology deployment policies
AU  - Dehler-Holland, Joris
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 54
IS  - 7
SP  - 105267
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/09/01/
SN  - 0048-7333
